Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:43.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared, my darlings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:45.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to advance, forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Advancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:50.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're our allies?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:52.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Left, forty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:54.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare the main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:01:58.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance, 400!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Load shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,HEAT Round!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.07,0:02:03.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:04.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Olga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:06.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:08.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been staring at this scope for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:10.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to die until I can take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:12.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Main cannon, ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:13.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:25.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna, signal the trailing forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:28.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,One enemy unit destroyed, follow our lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:29.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:31.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia, cover Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:38.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flashing, but it's not lightning. So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:40.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:50.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Three o'clock{\fscx300}-{\fscx100}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:23.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Ka...mi...ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:47.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Hi...go...ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:29.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Noel, nothing will get clean if you don't put effort in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:30.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:59.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This building is so cold in the winter, but it's great in summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:03.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Weren't Rio and Felicia in charge of laundry today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They seemed busy so they asked me to switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:07.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:09.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Felicia's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:13.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wasn't hungry, so we could eat it if we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:17.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:22.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing? Preparing dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:26.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what {\i1}are{\i0} you doing? You'll get in trouble for playing with food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:29.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not playing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Obon is today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's Obon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:36.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Fiesta des Lumières.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:36.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:37.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Fi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:42.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Fiesta des Lumières is a special Southern Helvetian event.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:48.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Derived from a local religion that believes the souls of the dead return to the present world for a short time in summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:51.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,To symbolize sending them back to Heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,lanterns are sent down the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:58.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,In other provinces, the same kind of festival is also known as "Obon".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:07.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So it's the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:11.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Souls of the dead return? Wait, what are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts are coming back, is that it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:15.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:19.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Lanterns? That sounds incredibly wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:21.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We only make fires in my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The dead go to Heaven and stay there forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:28.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Any left wandering on the surface are evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But the church{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:37.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lend us a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:41.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you two go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:45.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked delicious, so I bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:46.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,These as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:01.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your father and mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:10.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, it's well made.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:14.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Even the church acknowledges it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:16.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That Fi-something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:20.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet the main church would have a problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:22.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but we're in the countryside, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so lax.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:29.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,In my hometown, we make horses and cows out of cucumbers and eggplants,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:31.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,for our ancestors to ride upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:39.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, we dance to impart some solace to the returning ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:40.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making it as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:47.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I only watched last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:04.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our job to maintain good relations with the local residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:08.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't think about the weird things, it's only a pretty festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:10.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Filicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:25.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:39.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}My hand just slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:43.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}But it sure is rare for the Captain to be clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}That's Kanata's domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:45.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:51.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been quite hot for the last few days, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been sleeping well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a short break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:03.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:07.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's acting a little weird, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:12.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't finish her meal and used the food budget to buy watermelons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:15.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have a lot of things on her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:20.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to check on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:21.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:26.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has very private matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I've read the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:39.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:40.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:57.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:05.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Grip it firmly, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:17.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, a monster looking like the Captain jumps out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:28.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe that this ocean was full of life a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:35.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard that the world is ending slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:39.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,and that humans are going to become extinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:43.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Those... are just rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:47.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if those rumors are true,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:50.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,then just what are we fighting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:07.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:44.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideographs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:50.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:55.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could read your last words...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:58.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this from the old era?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:17.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Olga...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:22.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Martina...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:23.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:27.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only survivor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:35.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,...are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:37.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:42.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So there are still people living in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:44.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:54.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:59.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,...to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:08.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry we couldn't protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:30.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all remnants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:40.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The final breaths of humanity's struggle for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:42.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:47.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,...can never restore the world's prosperity as it once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just decide that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:52.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:56.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You should simply put an end to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:05.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Struggling for life within the despair of an apocalyptic world must be lonesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:07.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No. No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:13.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying life still has meaning in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:16.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:40.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:50.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm over here! I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:52.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:15.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:27.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If only our unit had arrived half a day earlier, this wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Your highness, Princess Iliya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wasn't expecting this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:40.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:45.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You totally ignored the Fiesta des Lumières last year, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:47.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the change of heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice color, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:59.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Treize. I bought it the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:02.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:04.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:12.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, she was everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:18.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to protect the country and its people like she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:22.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, sometimes I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:25.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a meaning to any of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:32.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So if she ever came back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted her to tell me the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm more worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:42.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's worrying about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:47.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,True, I guess I did made things a little awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:49.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I've failed as a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:53.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I{\fscx300}-{\fscx100} Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:59.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway! Don't shoulder everything yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:01.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I can at least listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:04.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:07.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll take you up on your offer and tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:14.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I gained weight this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:18.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I won't be able to wear my winter uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:24.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that eating only watermelons can help lose weight, so I'm trying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:26.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's wrong, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still playing dumb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were on the front lines at Vingt{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:39.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You must be thinking I was recalling that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:42.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:52.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:09.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You made one too, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:13.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not that I believe in "spirits" or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a mission, I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:19.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, who did you make yours for, Filicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,My old comrades,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:26.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,and a nameless soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:30.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a savior who made me realize what's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:32.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that person the reason why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:38.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia, if anything's bothering you, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:42.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I might not be of help...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:48.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I've made you worry, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:49.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:53.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:57.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to worry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:00.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always worried about me, Filicia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:02.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made you worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to worry about you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:08.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, I like you, Filicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:14.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And I love you too, Kana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:18.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to stay as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:22.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:25.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always telling us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:29.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,to not be afraid to share our feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that's an amazing thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:42.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:45.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:54.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You all... are so adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:07.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come again next year, my ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:16.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:29.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother... Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:42.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}Rio, you were asking about the meaning in this world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:43.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,715)}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:48.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Being the only survivor, I've always thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:52.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why I was the only one left alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:56.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,and what meaning there was to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:56.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Listen now, be careful not to fall over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:21:58.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've realized,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.14,0:22:02.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,that for us, this world must have no meaning in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.31,0:22:07.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:13.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it means we can find that meaning ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:22.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've already discovered the reason I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:26.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And after that, the Priest...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.73,0:22:27.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.83,0:22:30.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He sucked, so he asked Yumina...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:38.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever want those kids to experience the same thing I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:40.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.84,0:24:19.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next episode: Phone Duty - We Have an Emergency
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:18.24,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The radiance of this sky will carry to your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:28.55,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The melody you dreamed of is like serenity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:33.54,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}For your hands the dream is still far away, but
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:38.54,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}remember the voice so gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:51.23,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}when someone sang the chord of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:01:00.70,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The sound of the skies echoes high over all sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:11.34,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}Everything reflected in your eyes is the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:20.68,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}Not even the shedding of of tears can stop you here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:33.24,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}We're playing tomorrow in the light that rains without end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:51.02,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Resonate the feelings of love and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:54.11,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let's perform the important things
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:12.11,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I cried when I was happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:18.06,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I laughed when I was hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:27.37,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}But, they're all proof that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:31.51,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let's walk slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:33.36,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:37.46,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Tell me what you truly want
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:38.73,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}You're just my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:44.89,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Even if love and friendship change over time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:44.89,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1\3c&H5ECC69&}I know, You know little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.89,0:23:50.35,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I want them to echo forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.89,0:23:50.89,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1\3c&H5ECC69&}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:56.67,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Speaking endless words touched by love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.67,0:24:02.81,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}This is our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:07.44,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I can hear our harmony
